\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Filemon  
\mt2 Emoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Keliso kalu nowoęž‰ Filemon emoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰. Filemonaęž‰ ene madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu nowoęž‰, Onesimus e tamin amioęž‰ Filemonoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nai ane. E nai haęž‰naęž‰gaęž‰, amisaęž‰n nowa elena, Foęž‰l e oęž‰liaęž‰ dibolo aya galili. Onesimus e Foęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, e Keliso dotaęž‰gaęž‰, Foloęž‰ aęž‰na asuwaęž‰taęž‰len.  
\ip Foęž‰l e dibolowa silikiyoęž‰, moęž‰foęž‰s we Filemonboęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰. Filemon eyoęž‰ Onesimusoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, aole oęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1.1-2 \xt Kolo 4.17, 2Tim 2.3\x*Foęž‰l, ne Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ dibolo amiloęž‰ soęž‰l ne oęž‰liaęž‰ nao Timoti nainoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ gemoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\p To we nili mili nafa nanogoęž‰ negeleloęž‰ diaęž‰senoęž‰, Filemon, ge oęž‰liaęž‰ nado Abia oęž‰liaęž‰ negeleloęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰senoęž‰ Akibus oęž‰liaęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale gi ayamiloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ mandoęž‰ daęž‰baęž‰ yaęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰, moęž‰foęž‰s we gimoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.   
\p
\v 3 Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ nili Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ini haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 Filemon eloęž‰ man nafale dimidoęž‰woęž‰ we  
\p
\v 4-5 Giloęž‰ Yaęž‰su Alan amiloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene maliloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ne daęž‰daęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ nili Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, ge asulufoęž‰liki mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen.  
\v 6 Giloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa dowab amiloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafale nimoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰noęž‰ fanda asululimaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ ge Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt 2Kol 7.4\x*Ni nao, giyoęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ sagale alifelaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, giloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰ halale alitaki, sagale alifaęž‰.   
\s1 Onesimusoęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, Filemonboęž‰ sioęž‰  
\p
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Filemon, giloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ nowoęž‰ daęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu niyoęž‰ to halaidoęž‰woęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 9 Koęž‰sega Keliso kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen man giloęž‰woęž‰ ne asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ to halaidoęž‰woęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰laki, goęž‰noęž‰n asuloęž‰waęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki, asuloęž‰l. Ne anasoęž‰le dowakiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ dibolowa soęž‰l.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt 1Kol 4.15, Kolo 4.9\x*Ne dibolo ayamiloęž‰ soęž‰l wenamioęž‰, Onesimusoęž‰ Keliso dowabikiyoęž‰, e ni soęž‰wa oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giyoęž‰ Onesimus e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰kiyoęž‰, gemoęž‰ dabu boęž‰doęž‰l.  
\v 11 Tamin amioęž‰ Onesimus\f + \fr 1.11 \ft Onesimus aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we, asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen.\f* eyoęž‰ ge moęž‰asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ eyoęž‰ naęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 12 Ne Onesimus oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilig dowaki, e oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ e geloęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\v 13 Niyoęž‰ e moęž‰hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ne oęž‰liaęž‰ dowai kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, ne Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafaya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ dibolowa soęž‰l wenamioęž‰, giloęž‰ asuwaęž‰tan aumboęž‰, eyoęž‰ ne oęž‰li asuwaęž‰taęž‰liki melebabe.  
\v 14 Niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰sega, naęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ semoęž‰saefaęž‰ amioęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ giloęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰woęž‰, niyoęž‰ moęž‰dibodamaęž‰noęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n asuloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki asulab.  
\v 15 Ge oęž‰liaęž‰ Onesimus oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ hoęž‰len abol no amioęž‰loęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ ane aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰? Gaęž‰gdoęž‰ aloboęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, e geloęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ge oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ dofoęž‰ meleaęž‰ki goęž‰waęž‰le?  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1.16 \xt 1Tim 6.2\x*Onesimus e geloęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, e gi madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu dowaki, giyoęž‰ e madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalule aęž‰dowab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Niyoęž‰ Onesimusoęž‰ mada asulab koęž‰sega, e gi nanog dialikiyoęž‰, Alanaęž‰ wi amioęž‰ e gaoleyoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaliki, giyoęž‰ e mada alan asulumaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 17 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giyoęž‰ ne gi milile aęž‰laęž‰asulalega, Onesimus e geloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ ne yab amiloęž‰ sagaloęž‰ dowaęž‰sen oęž‰leaumboęž‰, emoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka sagalaęž‰bi.  
\v 18 Onesimus eyoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ halaboęž‰ dimidoęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, waęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dowoęž‰lalega, gemoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ noęž‰noęž‰n dugumiaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 19 Ne Foęž‰l, to we noęž‰noęž‰n dagileyaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l, â€śWaęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ hendele gemoęž‰woęž‰ dugumiaęž‰noęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰li saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Koęž‰sega ge to we asuluma. Giloęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰gi di aęž‰namioęž‰, nemoęž‰loęž‰ waęž‰l meaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ daęž‰lab.  
\v 20 Naęž‰noęž‰ Keliso amioęž‰ naole dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ man nafa we nemoęž‰woęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki asulab. Kelisowaęž‰ man nafa giloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ni asuloęž‰woęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 21 Niloęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ dabu boęž‰doęž‰l we, giyoęž‰ hendele dimidakiyoęž‰, man nafa noloęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰dimidamaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, moęž‰foęž‰s we gemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1.22 \xt Fili 1.25, 2.24\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nowoęž‰ we. Giloęž‰ Godemoęž‰loęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰len aumboęž‰ dimidaliki, ne geloęž‰ amioęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma miaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulab koęž‰loęž‰ giyoęž‰ uwoęž‰b nowoęž‰ ninoęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰lubi.  
\p Giyoęž‰ ne geloęž‰wa menaęž‰ki Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰, ne geloęž‰ amioęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma miaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ uwoęž‰b nowoęž‰ ninoęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰lubi.   
\s1 Sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰foęž‰  
\p
\v 23 \x - \xo 1.23 \xt Kolo 1.7\x*Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ dibolo amiloęž‰ sab nowoęž‰ Ebafelas, e ne oęž‰liaęž‰ wena siliki, eyoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ gemoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 1.24 \xt Kolo 4.10-14\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ negeleloęž‰ nanog dian kalu noloęž‰ Mak, Alistakus, Demas oęž‰liaęž‰ Luk iliyoęž‰loęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ sagaęž‰tab.   
\p
\v 25 Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi mama oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaęž‰biyoęž‰.   